data.description: This updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is located in the charming Southeast Portland neighborhood on a spacious corner lot. The home boasts modern finishes and features, including an open-concept living area, updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite counters and beautiful laminate flooring and updated bathrooms with new granite and laminate as well! With three bedrooms, plus a large family room there is ample space for a growing family or for use as a home office. The corner lot provides plenty of outdoor space for gardening, entertaining, or simply relaxing in the fresh air. Also of note is the huge RV parking space! This home is a must-see for anyone looking for a comfortable and stylish living space in a great location.
